InfoScreen - Class in froggerFrames
Represents the Information Screen of Frogger Game.
Singleton Design Pattern is applied to this class, so there is only one InfoScreen instance throughout the game.
InfoScreen(String) - Constructor for class froggerFrames.InfoScreen
This constructor will create an InfoScreen, displaying the instructions to play the game.
The constructor is declared private to ensure that no other classes can create another InfoScreen instance except itself.
